&lt;li&gt;An ace writer and content creator. A pro at developing the strategy and creative for client campaigns, including content calendars, mailers, landing pages, social memes/graphics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A highly organized client relations and project management pro&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A creative, collaborative multitasker who thrives in fast-paced, campaign-like environments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Skilled in digital organizing and communications with familiarity in online advertising, mobile strategy, and web design.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Possess knowledge of digital platforms and analytics to further client and campaign success.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You have at least 3-5 years of strategic communications experience in social justice, labor, advocacy, organizing, politics, or media, and you’re eager to make a difference for the public good.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Agency experience is a plus, but not required.&lt;/li&gt;
